{"tid":804114,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"作咗首gay佬詩","createTime":"2018-09-02T18:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T18:55:19.000Z","uid":131766,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7f0705eefde33dca2ffad5a4fa79d9a4ca7e9179","tid":804114,"uid":131766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T18:41:07.000Z","msg":"《家雄》      毒熊<br />\n十指緊扣，情心兩意。<br />\n許下承諾，再做情人。<br />\n今生之緣，三生有幸。<br />\n永不磨滅，永不忘記。<br />\n情義兩難，遠奔高飛。<br />\n世外桃源，唯兄同享。<br />\n鳥語花香，品酒談常。<br />\n白頭到老，攜手享安。<br />\n慶兄之存，慶兄之現。<br />\n今生之福，望兄銘記。<br />\n當天承諾，鐵記於心。<br />\n回首昔日，身戰累累。<br />\n今朝他日，兩老並存。<br />\n與世獨立，斷金取兄。<br />\n下世之緣，情比金堅。<br />\n合十雙手，衷心禱告。<br />\n吾與兄情，浪濤不息。"},{"pid":"49e7a909aaaec94bab66881f1e866be73bb6e950","tid":804114,"uid":131766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T18:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a9a4ada9380e23a95f5cdc6dfc7e6f2894e08d","tid":804114,"uid":131766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T18:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448e2cd48c0fd09bb5bc8ca484c8aa0320fc8fed","tid":804114,"uid":131766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T18:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eaae39d8a0a89cf518057b09adf5c2a6fcb7d53","tid":804114,"uid":131766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T18:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923acf3a389729c78c462e8274049eb8fc858ac2","tid":804114,"uid":44035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T18:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0f9edce862112f065f8070ab4a7c9baef1524f","tid":804114,"uid":131766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"923acf3a389729c78c462e8274049eb